    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior retains a nice shine, though you will find some minor stone chips and light surface scratches expected with age. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, showing only modest wear on the upholstery and touchpoints. It has been regularly serviced and drives smoothly, offering a great balance of quality and value for someone looking for a dependable daily driver.",
      "price": 36500.0,
